Always document changes done, so that the next agent or person that looks at this project understands whats going on. We have an AGENTS.md document that is for general documentation. I also want you to create .md files in subfolders and update those in regards to changes done, so we are aware of whats going on in those subfolders.

I also want you to update the Project Structure in the root AGENTS.md file when things are added or removed. Add CHANGES.md files to places where changes are done, do not add "Recent Updates" to the main Agents.md file in the root. 

File delegation: "_components" folders are meant to contain components that subfolders share. E.g. both the student and teacher in the (dashboard) folder share components, those shared components will be in the "_components" folder.